           woven by hand takes a solvent signature; auto-posting an unread pile bounces as a "bad check."
           Verified mechanic (headless): hand-woven -> solvent (100%); auto-posted -> bounced (0%);
           mostly-woven -> solvent (>=60%). Nothing is measured about the world; NO ACI is minted.
           Self-referential by design: this page is thread until a human weaves it by reading it.
